{% schema %}
  {
    
    "name": "Section 4",
    "tag": "section",
    "class": "gps-588442135225697219 gps gpsil",
    "settings": [{"type":"paragraph","content":"Section design by GemPages. [Click here to start design](https://admin.shopify.com/store/y1behc-h0/apps/gempages-cro/app/shopify/edit?pageType=GP_FUNNEL_PAGE&editorId=588441958863602491&sectionId=588442135225697219)"},{"type":"select","label":"Section Preload","id":"section_preload","options":[{"label":"On","value":"true"},{"label":"Off","value":"false"},{"label":"Off Lazy Script","value":"off_lazy_script"}],"default":"false"},{"type":"text","label":"Checksum","id":"checksum"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZLj2SvUDL_text","label":"ggZLj2SvUDL_text","default":"<p>Every day after your 35th birthday, something <i>subtle yet devastating</i> begins to fade inside you.</p><p><br>Not money from your account.<br>Not your health, not even your ambition.</p><p>Something deeper, <strong>the </strong><i><strong>energetic signature</strong></i><strong> that quietly pulled luck, focus, and opportunity toward you for decades.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You’ve probably felt it without understanding why.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The timing of life feels… off.</p><p><br>People who once lit up when you spoke now seem distracted.</p><p><br>Doors that used to open effortlessly stay shut.</p><p><br>Even your best ideas seem to drift away before the world notices.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And while you’re working harder than ever, younger, less experienced people are somehow <i>catching all <strong>the lucky breaks.</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>It’s not coincidence.</p><p><br>It’s not karma.</p><p><br>It’s <strong>physics,</strong> or rather, the silent breakdown of your body’s <i><strong>magnetic field of coherence.</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Researchers now confirm what Eastern adepts knew for millennia: your energetic field, the same one responsible for focus, attraction, and intuitive timing, begins to destabilize with age.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Once the frequency that fuels your attention and magnetism starts to distort, it’s as if life itself stops responding to you.</p><p><br>Opportunities <strong>don’t “see” you</strong> anymore.<br>People don’t <i>feel</i> your signal the way they used to.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The result?</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Millions of men and women past midlife feel like they’re pushing uphill, working twice as hard for half the rewards, while the world seems to flow effortlessly for others.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Western medicine calls it <strong>“aging.”</strong></p><p><br>Ancient Hermetic science called it <i>the <strong>Dissolution of the Signal.</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Different names.</p><p><br>Same truth.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>You are slowly losing the current that makes manifestation, prosperity, and purpose <i>work.</i></p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggXsXYldfVV_text","label":"ggXsXYldfVV_text","default":"<p><strong>But in 2025, something extraordinary is happening, quietly, almost secretly.</strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Across the world, men and women who once felt their “signal” fading are starting to reverse it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>They’re reporting things science can’t explain:<br>✨ Promotions after years of being overlooked.<br>✨ Unexpected financial windfalls.<br>✨ Relationships, &nbsp;and even health, suddenly reigniting.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Their secret?</p><p><br>It’s not a pill.</p><p><br>It’s not positive thinking.</p><p><br>And it’s definitely not financial advice.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>It’s a rediscovery, a 3,000-year-old understanding of how energy flows through the human body, and how to </strong><i><strong>restore the magnetic current that naturally weakens with age.</strong></i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>The wildest part?</p><p><br><strong><u>The solution costs less than your monthly coffee budget.</u></strong></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>But the true value isn’t in the cost.</p><p><br>It’s in what this discovery <i>rebuilds,</i> the same invisible frequency the ancients called <i>The Sovereign Signal.</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>Keep reading if you would like to:</strong></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p><p>✅ <strong>Uncover</strong> why so many over 40 are quietly “energetically bankrupt”, and how a decoded Egyptian sequence is helping them attract prosperity again.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>✅ <strong>Learn</strong> why CEOs, athletes, and even Wall Street elites are flying to Egypt, not for business, but for a single session with a hidden “frequency architect.”</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>✅ <strong>Witness</strong> how one father, after years of decline, used this reactivation ritual to turn debt into generational abundance.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>✅ <strong>Discover</strong> how a forgotten element, the same metal used in ancient initiation chambers, may help restore your prosperity field faster than any mindset or method.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggCD2JdlqCZ_text","label":"ggCD2JdlqCZ_text","default":"<p><span style=\"font-size:24px;\"><strong>The Secret That 17 Hedge Fund Titans Flew Across the World to Find</strong></span></p><p><br>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOuOecNqXI_text","label":"ggOuOecNqXI_text","default":"<p>On <strong>January 25th 2023</strong>, seventeen private jets descended on a private airstrip outside <strong>Luxor, Egypt, </strong>a strip of sand and stone surrounded by the shadow of ancient temples.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Inside those jets were some of the wealthiest individuals alive:tech billionaires, real-estate magnates, hedge-fund titans who could sway markets with a single word.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And yet, they hadn’t come for a deal, a merger, or a summit.<br>They’d come for <strong>a secret buried in the sands</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Not a modern investment secret…but one whispered about in forbidden Hermetic manuscripts. A secret said to restore the <i>energetic fortune field</i> that once made empires rise.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>For months, their fortunes had been crumbling in strange, unexplainable ways:<br>failed trades, sudden downturns, deals dissolving for no logical reason.<br>It was as if the invisible current that had guided their intuition had simply vanished.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Their destination was a newly unearthed chamber beneath the <strong>Temple of Hathor</strong>, where archeologists had uncovered an artifact known as <strong>The Codex of Light and Shadow, </strong>a stone vault etched with harmonic equations, believed to predate the Pyramids themselves.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Among the few researchers granted access was <strong>Amara Callen</strong>, a neuroscientist obsessed with bridging ancient Hermetic law and modern quantum biology.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>While the world’s elite came hoping to buy luck,<br>Amara saw something different: <i><strong>proof</strong>.</i></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Her team discovered that the inscriptions inside the Codex weren’t symbolic at all, they were <strong>frequency formulas</strong> designed to stabilize the human energy field.<br>Every line, every curve, every pattern corresponded to measurable electromagnetic ratios, a system for <i>restoring coherence</i> to the frequency that fuels focus, attraction, and vitality.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>In other words, what the ancients encoded wasn’t myth or religion, it was a <strong>scientific process for rebuilding the human signal</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>Amara spent twelve years decoding those formulas, testing them against real-world data, and found that they worked.</p><p><br>That research became the foundation of her manuscript,<i><strong>The Lost Laws of Manifestation,</strong></i> the first modern translation of the Codex.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>And while the billionaires flew home clutching fragments of sandstone as souvenirs, Amara realized the relic itself wasn’t the power.<br>The real secret was <strong>the law behind it, </strong>a living frequency principle that could be activated in any human being willing to relearn it.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>That discovery would quietly ignite a new chapter in human potential, and it’s the same discovery you’re about to explore in these pages.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggW5ReZhLFf_label","label":"ggW5ReZhLFf_label","default":"<p>CHECK AVAILABILITY&gt;&gt;</p>"}],
